cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

This paper involves natural language processing and computer vision, which are both covered by the cs.CL and cs.CV categories. The use of machine learning models also suggests the cs.AI category. The paper also involves resolving annotator disagreement, which could fall under the cs.LG category. Finally, the task of mapping natural language commands to executable commands in an image editing program could involve information retrieval techniques, making the cs.IR category a possibility.
